{com}. 
.         * Set the environment to make randomization replicable
.     isid ___index, sort
{txt}(data now sorted by {bf:___index})

{com}.     set  seed 208976  // bit.ly/stata-random set the random seed for replication 
{txt}
{com}.         
.         ********* Sample selection
.         ** check consent
.         keep if consentYN == 1  // 2 observations dropped
{txt}(2 observations deleted)

{com}.         // ignore attrition on 2 rejecation out of 2513 total observations
.         keep if !mi(Admin5Name)
{txt}(11 observations deleted)

{com}.         
.         tab phone_ownership, nol

   {txt}Does the {c |}
  household {c |}
have access {c |}
  to mobile {c |}
     phone? {c |}      Freq.     Percent        Cum.
